1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,601
Welcome to 4-7-8 breathing.

2
00:00:02,601 --> 00:00:07,524
This practice uses a longer exhale to
help the body settle.

3
00:00:16,524 --> 00:00:16,524
<break time="3s" />

4
00:00:16,524 --> 00:00:23,636
We will breathe in for four counts, hold
for seven counts, and breathe out for

5
00:00:23,636 --> 00:00:24,837
eight counts.

6
00:00:33,837 --> 00:00:33,837
<break time="3s" />

7
00:00:33,837 --> 00:00:39,344
If holding your breath does not feel
good, you can shorten the hold or simply

8
00:00:39,344 --> 00:00:40,431
breathe gently.

9
00:00:49,431 --> 00:00:49,431
<break time="3s" />

10
00:00:49,431 --> 00:00:53,750
Let this be supportive, not forced.

11
00:00:53,750 --> 00:00:57,233
Begin by sitting or lying comfortably.

12
00:00:57,233 --> 00:00:59,509
Let your shoulders soften.

13
00:00:59,509 --> 00:01:01,320
Let your jaw loosen.

14
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:03,549
Take one natural breath in.

15
00:01:03,549 --> 00:01:05,174
And let it out.

16
00:01:05,174 --> 00:01:07,078
Now we’ll begin.

17
00:01:07,078 --> 00:01:08,796
Breathe in.

18
00:01:17,796 --> 00:01:17,796
<break time="3s" />

19
00:01:17,796 --> 00:01:18,400
One.

20
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:19,422
Two.

21
00:01:19,422 --> 00:01:20,072
Three.

22
00:01:20,072 --> 00:01:20,722
Four.

23
00:01:20,722 --> 00:01:22,022
Hold.

24
00:01:31,022 --> 00:01:31,022
<break time="3s" />

25
00:01:31,022 --> 00:01:31,626
One.

26
00:01:31,626 --> 00:01:32,323
Two.

27
00:01:32,323 --> 00:01:32,787
Three.

28
00:01:32,787 --> 00:01:33,669
Four.

29
00:01:33,669 --> 00:01:34,505
Five.

30
00:01:34,505 --> 00:01:34,969
Six.

31
00:01:34,969 --> 00:01:36,548
Seven.

32
00:01:36,548 --> 00:01:37,802
Exhale.

33
00:01:46,802 --> 00:01:46,802
<break time="3s" />

34
00:01:46,802 --> 00:01:47,174
One.

35
00:01:47,174 --> 00:01:47,871
Two.

36
00:01:47,871 --> 00:01:48,660
Three.

37
00:01:48,660 --> 00:01:49,867
Four.

38
00:01:49,867 --> 00:01:50,656
Five.

39
00:01:50,656 --> 00:01:51,399
Six.

40
00:01:51,399 --> 00:01:51,910
Seven.

41
00:01:51,910 --> 00:01:52,282
Eight.

42
00:01:52,282 --> 00:01:53,304
Again.

43
00:01:53,304 --> 00:01:54,790
Breathe in.

44
00:02:03,790 --> 00:02:03,790
<break time="3s" />

45
00:02:03,790 --> 00:02:04,162
One.

46
00:02:04,162 --> 00:02:04,812
Two.

47
00:02:04,812 --> 00:02:05,416
Three.

48
00:02:05,416 --> 00:02:06,670
Four.

49
00:02:06,670 --> 00:02:08,063
Hold.

50
00:02:17,063 --> 00:02:17,063
<break time="3s" />

51
00:02:17,063 --> 00:02:17,713
One.

52
00:02:17,713 --> 00:02:18,270
Two.

53
00:02:18,270 --> 00:02:18,734
Three.

54
00:02:18,734 --> 00:02:19,709
Four.

55
00:02:19,709 --> 00:02:21,195
Five.

56
00:02:21,195 --> 00:02:22,728
Six.

57
00:02:22,728 --> 00:02:24,075
Seven.

58
00:02:24,075 --> 00:02:25,050
Exhale.

59
00:02:34,050 --> 00:02:34,050
<break time="3s" />

60
00:02:34,050 --> 00:02:34,422
One.

61
00:02:34,422 --> 00:02:34,933
Two.

62
00:02:34,933 --> 00:02:35,630
Three.

63
00:02:35,630 --> 00:02:36,512
Four.

64
00:02:36,512 --> 00:02:37,209
Five.

65
00:02:37,209 --> 00:02:37,627
Six.

66
00:02:37,627 --> 00:02:39,160
Seven.

67
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:39,996
Eight.

68
00:02:39,996 --> 00:02:43,618
Let the exhale be slow and easy.

69
00:02:52,618 --> 00:02:52,618
<break time="3s" />

70
00:02:52,618 --> 00:02:53,733
Again.

71
00:02:53,733 --> 00:02:54,755
Inhale.

72
00:03:03,755 --> 00:03:03,755
<break time="3s" />

73
00:03:03,755 --> 00:03:04,730
One.

74
00:03:04,730 --> 00:03:05,287
Two.

75
00:03:05,287 --> 00:03:06,402
Three.

76
00:03:06,402 --> 00:03:07,145
Four.

77
00:03:07,145 --> 00:03:08,631
Hold.

78
00:03:17,631 --> 00:03:17,631
<break time="3s" />

79
00:03:17,631 --> 00:03:18,142
One.

80
00:03:18,142 --> 00:03:18,746
Two.

81
00:03:18,746 --> 00:03:19,443
Three.

82
00:03:19,443 --> 00:03:20,140
Four.

83
00:03:20,140 --> 00:03:20,929
Five.

84
00:03:20,929 --> 00:03:21,393
Six.

85
00:03:21,393 --> 00:03:22,182
Seven.

86
00:03:22,182 --> 00:03:23,389
Exhale.

87
00:03:32,389 --> 00:03:32,389
<break time="3s" />

88
00:03:32,389 --> 00:03:33,132
One.

89
00:03:33,132 --> 00:03:34,107
Two.

90
00:03:34,107 --> 00:03:34,664
Three.

91
00:03:34,664 --> 00:03:35,825
Four.

92
00:03:35,825 --> 00:03:36,382
Five.

93
00:03:36,382 --> 00:03:36,800
Six.

94
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,100
Seven.

95
00:03:38,100 --> 00:03:39,633
Eight.

96
00:03:39,633 --> 00:03:43,998
If you need to breathe normally at any
time, do that.

97
00:03:43,998 --> 00:03:46,970
Your body knows what it needs.

98
00:03:46,970 --> 00:03:48,363
Again.

99
00:03:48,363 --> 00:03:49,756
Breathe in.

100
00:03:58,756 --> 00:03:58,756
<break time="3s" />

101
00:03:58,756 --> 00:03:59,406
One.

102
00:03:59,406 --> 00:04:00,010
Two.

103
00:04:00,010 --> 00:04:00,799
Three.

104
00:04:00,799 --> 00:04:02,053
Four.

105
00:04:02,053 --> 00:04:03,307
Hold.

106
00:04:12,307 --> 00:04:12,307
<break time="3s" />

107
00:04:12,307 --> 00:04:13,050
One.

108
00:04:13,050 --> 00:04:13,375
Two.

109
00:04:13,375 --> 00:04:14,722
Three.

110
00:04:14,722 --> 00:04:15,372
Four.

111
00:04:15,372 --> 00:04:16,765
Five.

112
00:04:16,765 --> 00:04:17,183
Six.

113
00:04:17,183 --> 00:04:18,530
Seven.

114
00:04:18,530 --> 00:04:20,155
Exhale.

115
00:04:29,155 --> 00:04:29,155
<break time="3s" />

116
00:04:29,155 --> 00:04:29,898
One.

117
00:04:29,898 --> 00:04:30,827
Two.

118
00:04:30,827 --> 00:04:31,338
Three.

119
00:04:31,338 --> 00:04:32,638
Four.

120
00:04:32,638 --> 00:04:34,171
Five.

121
00:04:34,171 --> 00:04:34,543
Six.

122
00:04:34,543 --> 00:04:35,147
Seven.

123
00:04:35,147 --> 00:04:36,215
Eight.

124
00:04:36,215 --> 00:04:38,630
Now let’s do a few quieter rounds.

125
00:04:38,630 --> 00:04:41,277
Breathe in for four.

126
00:04:50,277 --> 00:04:50,277
<break time="3s" />

127
00:04:50,277 --> 00:04:51,902
Hold for seven.

128
00:05:00,902 --> 00:05:00,902
<break time="3s" />

129
00:05:00,902 --> 00:05:02,527
Exhale for eight.

130
00:05:11,527 --> 00:05:11,527
<break time="3s" />

131
00:05:11,527 --> 00:05:12,781
Again.

132
00:05:12,781 --> 00:05:14,314
Inhale.

133
00:05:23,314 --> 00:05:23,314
<break time="3s" />

134
00:05:23,314 --> 00:05:24,475
Hold.

135
00:05:33,475 --> 00:05:33,475
<break time="3s" />

136
00:05:33,475 --> 00:05:34,775
Exhale.

137
00:05:43,775 --> 00:05:43,775
<break time="3s" />

138
00:05:43,775 --> 00:05:45,772
One more round.

139
00:05:45,772 --> 00:05:46,701
Inhale.

140
00:05:55,701 --> 00:05:55,701
<break time="3s" />

141
00:05:55,701 --> 00:05:56,769
Hold.

142
00:06:05,769 --> 00:06:05,769
<break time="3s" />

143
00:06:05,769 --> 00:06:07,348
Exhale.

144
00:06:16,348 --> 00:06:16,348
<break time="3s" />

145
00:06:16,348 --> 00:06:18,298
Now release the counting.

146
00:06:18,298 --> 00:06:21,409
Let your breath return to its natural
rhythm.

147
00:06:30,409 --> 00:06:30,409
<break time="3s" />

148
00:06:30,409 --> 00:06:31,756
Notice your body.

149
00:06:43,756 --> 00:06:43,756
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

150
00:06:43,756 --> 00:06:46,357
Notice whether anything has shifted.

151
00:06:46,357 --> 00:06:48,633
Maybe there is more calm.

152
00:06:48,633 --> 00:06:50,491
Maybe there is resistance.

153
00:06:50,491 --> 00:06:53,556
Maybe there is no obvious change.

154
00:06:53,556 --> 00:06:56,110
All of that is okay.

155
00:06:56,110 --> 00:06:59,361
Take one final natural breath in.

156
00:06:59,361 --> 00:07:01,126
And let it out.

157
00:07:01,126 --> 00:07:03,587
When you are ready, return to the room.

